      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Sprinkle the pizza[s] with the <strong>grated cheese </strong>then top with the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>green chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 13-15 min or until the cheese has melted and the base is crisp – this is your <strong>chicken thigh fajita pizza</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
